  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2579710/extras/f342e4614c045017be44dbf7c31ade62.poster.avif?t=1701975008\" width=614 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2579710/extras/f342e4614c045017be44dbf7c31ade62.webm?t=1701975008\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2579710/extras/f342e4614c045017be44dbf7c31ade62.mp4?t=1701975008\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Airplanes are a very convenient means of transportation, but not if you are outside of it.</strong><br>However, the presence of a grappling hook can easily eliminate this disadvantage. <br>You have to go through a variety of levels, clinging to planes falling apart in the air, using a grappling hook and various abilities.<br><br>Explosions, flying, a sense of speed, and a veeery long grappling hook are waiting for you in Aerodangle!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2579710/extras/f342e4614c045017be44dbf7c31ade62.poster.avif?t=1701975008\" width=614 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2579710/extras/f342e4614c045017be44dbf7c31ade62.webm?t=1701975008\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2579710/extras/f342e4614c045017be44dbf7c31ade62.mp4?t=1701975008\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Airplanes are a very convenient means of transportation, but not if you are outside of it.</strong><br>However, the presence of a grappling hook can easily eliminate this disadvantage. <br>You have to go through a variety of levels, clinging to planes falling apart in the air, using a grappling hook and various abilities.<br><br>Explosions, flying, a sense of speed, and a veeery long grappling hook are waiting for you in Aerodangle!",
